      <title>特朗普称仍考虑征收 10% 关税，中国股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/chinese-stocks-fall-after-trump-says-10-tariffs-still-on-table</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示仍在考虑对中国商品征收 10% 关税的威胁，中国股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/chinese-stocks-fall-after-trump-says-10-tariffs-still-on-table</guid>
